Of those, my guess for good ones against Riven would probably include {{champion:31}} (good damage and sustain, hard to burst) {{champion:122}} (she can't all in you because you crush everything that gets in melee range) {{champion:114}} (I have never seen a Fiora lose this matchup, even if the Fiora sucks) {{champion:86}} (known counter pick) {{champion:150}} (good against all ins, great damage and durability, good poke) {{champion:54}} (counters AD really well, good scaling damage even when tank) {{champion:2}} (out-bullies everyone else in lane, you can usually kill her if she tries to all in you) {{champion:27}} (ydgaf if she kills you, you're singed, all you need to do is run away and let her kill herself while you hard push) {{champion:48}} (you steal AD, armor, MR, and health, you out-bully and out sustain her, she can't duel you late game) {{champion:6}} (counters AD assassin types wonderfully) {{champion:83}} (counters life itself. Even if she all-ins you, you can use your ult to almost always get a revenge kill, and you don't need to be 4 and 0 to be relevant late game) {{champion:33}} (stack armor for damages, you can run away from her if she chases, taunt under tower, and get so stupid tanky that she'll never kill you) {{champion:44}} (stack armor, sustain for days, hard CC if she starts an all-in, moderate burst, excellent ways of keeping Riven from killing your team)
